VALUES
  ('social-worker-moex-00301', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關「英美慈善組織會社（CharityOrganizationSociety,COS）」的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["為當代社區組織的精神與做法奠定發展的基礎", "主要在糾正當時慈善組織缺乏聯繫協調的亂象，企圖整合救濟資源，以杜絕職業乞丐", "慈善組織會社派「親善訪問員」訪問申請救濟者，被視為是社會個案工作的前身", "提出救濟金的發放是依照家庭規模的大小加以計算，制定「史賓漢蘭制度（Speenhamland System）」"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cfb12f7e18eb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e27a949c51a2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00302', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '臺灣社會工作的發展由日本從西方輾轉移植來臺，再由西方強勢國家擴散過來。若以本土化觀點 看待臺灣社會工作，下列敘述何者正確？', '["社會工作者應與案主保持正式專業關係，不可接受案主的回饋，如送禮等，如此才能與案主建 立良好關係", "臺灣社會工作發展迄今已有完整的本土化教材", "中華文化的基本價值和自我觀影響案主因應方式和求助行為模式", "不論西方或是臺灣的案主在因應方式或是求助行為模式都是類似的。因此，社會工作者不需要 特別考量文化議題"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cfb12f7e18eb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e27a949c51a2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00303', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是英國伊莉莎白43號法案之重要變革內容？', '["區分具工作能力與無工作能力的貧民", "每一教區設立濟貧監察員", "分區辦理貧民救濟工作", "強調政府責任"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cfb12f7e18eb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e27a949c51a2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00304', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '89歲獨居的服務對象，因中風入院治療後，經醫療團隊評估已可出院，社會工作者協助其返家居 住，並提供服務對象獨立生活照顧之相關服務。社工的做法屬於下列何種服務？', '["在地老化", "就地合法", "家庭自決", "獨立自救"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cfb12f7e18eb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e27a949c51a2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00305', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關社會工作特質的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["社會工作強調社區資源的運用", "社會工作重視人的一致性", "社會工作強調個人的劣勢", "社會工作強調「權力」是助人的關鍵"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cfb12f7e18eb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e27a949c51a2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00306', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作是一項助人專業，它幫助個人、團體、社區增強或恢復其社會功能，這裡指的「社會功 能」，下列何者為錯誤？', '["滿意的生活角色扮演", "與他人建立正向的關係", "有自我價值感", "解決個人精神層面的議題"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cfb12f7e18eb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e27a949c51a2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00307', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作者向高中生介紹社會工作學系，下列敘述何者貼近社會工作的專業服務基礎？', '["社會工作價值觀與主流社會價值是一致的", "社會工作服務是以科學與價值為基礎的藝術", "社會工作服務地點以機構的辦公室與會談室為限", "社會工作重視理論，服務運用的知識都經過驗證"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cfb12f7e18eb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e27a949c51a2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00308', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '從日本引進的「減法照顧－提供長者剛剛好需要的照顧，不是照顧者認為該提供的照顧」，此精神 與下列何種社會工作理念敘述最為接近？', '["聚焦長者還擁有能力的優勢觀點", "重視家庭照顧者負荷的系統觀點", "回應長者不同性格的個別化照顧思考", "照顧長者非一家之力，需動員社區資源"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cfb12f7e18eb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e27a949c51a2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00309', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '「充權」案主是社會工作者的工作目標，下列何者屬於案主消權？①與拒絕申請保護令案主，討', '["說服從事季節性工作案主，接受職訓找薪水穩定的工作", "與獨居老人 討論安裝緊急救援系統，以降低獨居風險", "說服未婚懷孕青少女要出養嬰兒，才能接續完成高 中學業", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cfb12f7e18eb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e27a949c51a2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00310', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Adams（2010）指出社會工作實務主要有三大面向工作。其中創造工作之內涵，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["跳脫例行性與程序性工作", "綜理不同情境的訊息", "適時地參與社會行動", "分析複雜情境和問題"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cfb12f7e18eb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e27a949c51a2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL)
